  profile?: string(name='profile', description='When you set `cluster_type` to `ManagedKubernetes` (ACK managed cluster types), you can further specify the cluster subtype.
- `Default`: ACK managed cluster, including ACK clusters (Pro and Basic).
- `Edge`: ACK Edge cluster, including ACK Edge clusters (Pro and Basic).
