Default value: `release`.', example='release'),
    securityGroupId?: string(name='security_group_id', description='The security group ID of the node pool. Use either this parameter or `security_group_ids`. We recommend that you use `security_group_ids`.', example='sg-wz9a8g2mt6x5llu0****', deprecated=true),
